<a href="/review/createreview/{{spot._id}}">Click me to create a review for this vacation spot!</a>

<p>Name: {{spot.name}}</p>
<p>Description: {{spot.description}}</p>
<p>City: {{spot.city}}</p>
<p>Region/State: {{spot.region}}</p>
<p>Country: {{spot.country}}</p>
<p>Continent: {{spot.continent}}</p>
<p>Overall Rating: {{spot.overallRating}}</p>
<p>Food Rating: {{spot.foodRating}}</p>
<p>Safety Rating: {{spot.safetyRating}}</p>
<p>Activity Rating: {{spot.activityRating}}</p>

{{#if spot.reviews.length}}
    <ol>
        {{#each spot.reviews}}
            <li>
                <p>Review: {{review}}</p>
                <a href="/review/{{_id}}">Click me to see this review</a>
                
            </li>
        {{/each}}
    </ol>
{{else}}
    <p class="not-found">We're sorry, but no reviews were for this vacation spot.</p>
{{/if}}

<hr />

<section class="qa-section">
  <h2>Q&amp;A</h2>
  <dl class="qa-list">
    <dt>Q: What’s the best time of year to visit?</dt>
    <dd>A: Late spring (May–June) offers mild weather and fewer crowds.</dd>

    <dt>Q: Are there lodging options nearby?</dt>
    <dd>A: Yes, hotels and guesthouses are typically within a 1 km radius of the main attractions.</dd>

    <dt>Q: What’s the typical daily cost?</dt>
    <dd>A: Expect to spend around $100–$150 per day, including meals and basic activities.</dd>
  </dl>
</section>